About:

  HOCR WWW is a web interface to libhocr, Hebrew character recognition library
  http://hocr.berlios.de

WARNING: THIS IS *NOT* A SECURE SERVICE, DO NOT INSTALL ON SYSTEMS WITH WEB ACCES

Install:
  1) install apache web server with php module on your server system.
  3) install ImageMagic and hocr on your server system
  4) configure the web server maximum upload file size
  5) copy the contents of libhocr/www directory to your web page.
  6) make sure the web server user (on debian www-data) 
      have write permissions on the install directory.

